},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","type":"topic","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/foregroundStyle(_:)":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Applies a ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"foreground style","type":"text"}]},{"text":" on the current view by using the given tokens of colors.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Uses the current color scheme so as to load the suitable color to apply in the end","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/foregroundStyle(_:)","title":"foregroundStyle(_:)","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip\/foregroundstyle(_:)","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"foregroundStyle","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken","preciseIdentifie